properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 11 at 4:07PM AKST until February 12 at 12:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 6
inches.

* WHERE...Juneau.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to noon AKST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning commute.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Wet snow will be difficult to manage. Rain
will mix in with the snow late Wednesday morning.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO NOON AKST WEDNESDAY
